  ],
  "remarks": "JSC RT-Techpriemka is a Russian military industry company. Under an agreement with the Russian Ministry of Defence, the company provides certification services for components dedicated to military industry companies. Also, JSC RT-Techpriemka produces metal alloys (for example, VNS9-Sh type) for companies that produce Mi-26, Mi-28 and Ka-52 helicopters. Mi-26, Mi-28 and Ka-52 helicopters are used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
